    <p>Easy! Send us a message through <a href="/messages/new" alt="contact form" target="_blank">the contact form</a> and we'll let you know what we need. We can also register you for business alerts.</p>

  <h2>How do I get my store listed on CONSIGN.NYC?</h2></h2>

    <p>Send us a message through <a href="/messages/new" alt="contact form" target="_blank">the contact form</a> and we'll consider your store for inclusion.</p>

  <h2>How do I sign up for the mailing list?</h2>

    <p>Easy! Simply <%= link_to "register with the site", new_user_registration_path %> and you'll automatically be added to the mailing list. Newsletters may include new site content, photos and special offers.</p>

